## Assistant Rules
- After completing a significant logical block (feature, page, widget, entity, service, or cross-cutting change), add an entry to `docs/FEATURES.md`.
- Entry format: date, name, short description, affected modules.

## Where to store documentation
- Backend architecture: `docs/architecture/backend.md`
- Admin frontend architecture: `docs/architecture/frontend-admin.md`
- Client frontend architecture: `docs/architecture/frontend-client.md`
- Guards/auth: `docs/architecture/guards.md`
- Database design: `docs/database/design.md`
- Feature log: `docs/FEATURES.md`

## Documentation index
- When adding/removing docs, update `docs/README.md`.
